elliptic-secp256k1.js is based on secp256k1-node, which is released under the
MIT license by the licesecp256k1-node contributors. Its license complete license can be found here: https://github.com/cryptocoinjs/secp256k1-node/blob/2f1c956d71c39e5667e6285a6dafc15ce28e86f0/LICENSE

scryptsy-without-crypto.js is based on scryptsy, which is released under the
MIT license by the cryptocoinjs. Its license complete license can be found here: https://github.com/cryptocoinjs/scryptsy/blob/395c3b09b21e06ea4a6cc2933e046c0984a414c5/LICENSE

hdkey-without-crypto.js is based on hdkey, which is released under the
MIT license by the cryptocoinjs. Its license complete license can be found here: https://github.com/cryptocoinjs/hdkey/blob/87d5495ac8e4dfe9917ddcebf6788ce69c0695ff/LICENSE

